CHANGELOG
---------

Version 1.2, July 6, 2009
--------------------------
* Idle detection - timer will pause during more than 3 min of inactivity
* Reset timer by clicking time
* Added feedback link

Version 1.1, June 21, 2009
--------------------------
* Trimmed UI
* Added visual feedback when reporting time
* Removed debugging buttons
* Widget now shows back when initialized as it should
* Minor bug fixes
* Added CHANGELOG for future reference

Version 1.0, June 19, 2009
--------------------------
* New UI
* Much faster login process
* Several bug fixes

Version 0.9
